comment: * Encapsulates results of a single profiling request operation.

variables.name: ERROR_NONE
variables.comment: The request was executed and succeeded.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_RATE_LIMIT_SYSTEM
variables.comment: The request was denied due to system level rate limiting.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_RATE_LIMIT_PROCESS
variables.comment: The request was denied due to process level rate limiting.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_PROFILING_IN_PROGRESS
variables.comment: The request was denied due to profiling already in progress.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_EXECUTING
variables.comment: The request was executed and failed for a reason not specified below.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_POST_PROCESSING
variables.comment: The request was executed but post processing failed and the result was discarded.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_NO_DISK_SPACE
variables.comment: The request was executed and failed due to a lack of disk space.

variables.name: ERROR_FAILED_INVALID_REQUEST
variables.comment: The request failed due to invalid ProfilingRequest.

variables.name: ERROR_UNKNOWN
variables.comment: The request was denied or failed for an unspecified reason.

methods.comment: * The result ErrorCode for the profiling request indicating the failure reason if applicable.

methods.comment:
* The file path of the profiling result data.
     *
     * Will be null if {@see #getErrorCode} returns code other than {@see #ERROR_NONE}.

methods.name: public String getTag()
methods.comment: * The tag defined by the caller at request time.

methods.comment: * Additional details about failures that occurred, if applicable.
